              <li>Restriction: B.A. Faculty Program in Environment, B.A.&amp;Sc. Faculty Program in Environment , B.Sc.(Ag.Env.Sc.) and B.Sc. Major in Environment, and Diploma in Environment.</li>
            </ul>
      </div>

